    • Booking

      public Booking(String bookingId, String userId, String slotId, String gymId, LocalDate bookingDate, String status, LocalDateTime createdAt, BookingDetails bookingDetails)
      Instantiates a new booking with the specified details.
      Parameters:
      bookingId - the unique identifier for the booking
      userId - the identifier of the user who made the booking
      slotId - the identifier of the gym slot booked
      gymId - the identifier of the gym where the booking is made
      bookingDate - the date of the booking
      status - the current status of the booking
      createdAt - the timestamp when the booking was created
      bookingDetails - additional details related to the booking
